      "writtenOn": "2021-01-28T19:58:50Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think it would give us more reliability and resistance to flakes, but it may not be worth the effort.\n\nSo we don\u0027t run any tests in parallel?  Seems like that would mess with the setting/unsetting of environment variables.",
      "parentUuid": "d81464b2_e0b1eebd",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 192,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 192,
        "endChar": 42
      },
      "revId": "b44554ec73ea4a02ef16de522c81a6e70990911e",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02"
    },
    {
      "unresolved": true,
      "key": {
        "uuid": "17ffad69_819a3cf7",
